<br>
   No one had noticed one more body out their going over the corpses. <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Guess Maelgroth, had this thing set up pretty tight, those old houses wouldn't be at each other's throats if not for whatever he's been doing to rile them up.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> she decided as she slipped back inside the estate while everyone was preoccupied with the results of the fighting. As she came inside she found herself face to face with her employer.<br>
